@startuml fluxo-agente
title Fluxo do agente — briefing vira tarefas no quadro
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName sans-serif

actor "Agente de IA" as Ag
participant "API Maestro" as API
database "MySQL" as DB

== Refino: gera a doc ==
Ag -> API : POST /projects/:id/documents\n(type=SPEC, body markdown)\nx-api-key
API -> DB : grava Document
API --> Ag : 201 doc criada

== Decompose: cria as tarefas ==
Ag -> API : POST /tasks/bulk\n(tarefas + subtarefas aninhadas)\nIdempotency-Key
API -> DB : cria tarefas/subtarefas (transação)
API -> DB : grava ActivityLog (via agente)
API --> Ag : 201 tarefas criadas (GAV-1..n)

== Execução: move no quadro ==
Ag -> API : GET /tasks?status=A fazer&assignee=me
API --> Ag : lista de tarefas
Ag -> API : POST /tasks/GAV-1/move {coluna: Fazendo}
API -> DB : atualiza coluna + ActivityLog
API --> Ag : 200 ok
Ag -> API : POST /tasks/GAV-1/comments\n{body: "PR aberto: <link>"}
API --> Ag : 201 comentário
@enduml
